<p><span style="font-size:1.3rem;">The <a href="https://ibc.oarc.science">Institute for Biblical Content</a> maintains and makes available online a number of multilingual resources and tools aimed at helping researchers who work with biblical text. All this resources are inter-linked.</span></p>

